New ➝ Open ➝ Assigned ➝ In Progress ➝ Fixed ➝ Retest ➝ Closed
                     ↘                     ↘
                     Rejected           Reopened


| Stage            | Jira Status (Customizable)        |
| ---------------- | --------------------------------- |
| New              | To Do / New                       |
| Open             | Open                              |
| Assigned         | Assigned                          |
| In Progress      | In Progress                       |
| Fixed            | Resolved / Fixed                  |
| Ready for Retest | Ready for QA                      |
| Closed           | Done / Closed                     |
| Reopened         | Reopened                          |
| Rejected         | Won’t Fix / Duplicate / Not a Bug |

